"v. 埋伏，伏击 无 v. 埋伏(从隐蔽中攻击) 【记】way, lay躺: 在路边躺着伏击. Waylaid是waylay的过去式及过去分词 【类】wary: gulled[duped] = exacting: satisfied = vigilant: ambushed[entrapped, waylaid]谨慎的不易被骗 = 挑剔的不易被满足 = 警觉的不易中埋伏 【记】way lay 躺在路上 waylay (v.)  ""to ambush,"" 1510s, from way (n.) + lay (v.), on model of Middle Low German, Middle Dutch wegelagen ""besetting of ways, lying in wait with evil or hostile intent along public ways."" Related: Waylaid; waylaying."
